A simple postfix syntax numeric calculator

Supported:
 - nonnegative integer constants
 - the binary operators + - * /
 - whitespace is optional when not needed to separate constants

Compile with
  make READLINE=1
if you have GNU readline development files installed.

Compile with
  make
otherwise.

The code is intended to be standard C99.


